\c 3
\nb
\v 1 Kwakukhona-ke impi isikhathi eside phakathi kwendlu kaSawuli lendlu kaDavida; kodwa uDavida waya eqina, kodwa indlu kaSawuli yaya isiba buthakathaka.
\s Amadodana kaDavida
\p
\v 2 Kwasekuzalelwa uDavida amadodana eHebroni\x + 1 Lan. 3.1-4.\x*; lezibulo lakhe lalinguAmnoni kaAhinowama umJizereyelikazi\x + 1 Sam. 25.43.\x*;
\v 3 leyesibili yakhe yayinguKileyabi kaAbigayili umkaNabali umKharmeli; eyesithathu yayinguAbisalomu indodana kaMahaka indodakazi kaTalimayi, inkosi yeGeshuri\x + 14.23,32. 15.8. Dute. 3.14. 1 Lan. 2.23.\x*;
\v 4 leyesine yayinguAdonija indodana kaHagithi\x + 1 Kho. 1.5.\x*; leyesihlanu yayinguShefathiya indodana kaAbithali;
\v 5 leyesithupha yayinguIthereyamu kaEgila, umkaDavida. Laba bazalelwa uDavida eHebroni.
\s Ukuvumelana kukaDavida loAbhineri
\p
\v 6 Kwasekusithi kuselempi phakathi kwendlu kaSawuli lendlu kaDavida, uAbhineri waziqinisa endlini kaSawuli.
\v 7 Njalo uSawuli wayelomfazi omncane, obizo lakhe lalinguRizipha indodakazi kaAya\x + 21.8,10.\x*; \add uIshiboshethi\add* wasesithi kuAbhineri: Ungeneleni emfazini omncane kababa\x + 16.21.\x*?
\v 8 UAbhineri wasethukuthela kakhulu ngenxa yamazwi kaIshiboshethi, wathi: Ngilikhanda lenja yini mina ongokaJuda? Lamuhla ngenzela indlu kaSawuli uyihlo umusa, kubafowabo, lakubangane bakhe, kangikunikelanga esandleni sikaDavida, ukuthi ungibeka icala ngowesifazana lamuhla\x + 9.8. 16.9. Dute. 23.18. 1 Sam. 17.43. 24.14. 2 Kho. 8.13.\x*?
\v 9 UNkulunkulu enze njalo kuAbhineri\x + 3.35. Ruthe 1.17.\x*, engezelele ngokunjalo kuye, ngeqiniso, njengoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ifungile kuDavida, qotho, ngizakwenza njalo kuye\x + 1 Sam. 15.28. 16.1,12. 28.17. 1 Lan. 12.23.\x*,
\v 10 ukudlulisa umbuso usuka endlini kaSawuli, lokumisa isihlalo sobukhosi sikaDavida phezu kukaIsrayeli laphezu kukaJuda, kusukela koDani kuze kufike eBherishebha\x + 17.11. 24.2,15. Hlu. 20.1. 1 Sam. 3.20. 1 Kho. 4.25.\x*.
\v 11 Njalo wayengelakumphendula uAbhineri ngalizwi futhi, ngoba wayemesaba.
\p
\v 12 UAbhineri wasethuma izithunywa kuDavida esikhundleni sakhe, esithi: Ngelikabani ilizwe? Esithi: Yenza isivumelwano sakho lami; khangela-ke, isandla sami sizakuba lawe ukuphendulela uIsrayeli wonke kuwe.
\v 13 Wasesithi: Kulungile; mina ngizakwenza isivumelwano lawe, kodwa yinye into engiyifuna kuwe, ngeyokuthi kawuyikubona ubuso bami\x + Gen. 43.3.\x*, ngaphandle kokuthi ulethe kuqala uMikhali indodakazi kaSawuli, lapho usizabona ubuso bami\x + 1 Sam. 14.49.\x*.
\v 14 UDavida wasethuma izithunywa kuIshiboshethi indodana kaSawuli, esithi: \add Ngi\add*nika umkami uMikhali engamgana ngamajwabu aphambili alikhulu amaFilisti\x + 1 Sam. 18.25,27.\x*.
\v 15 UIshiboshethi wasethumela, wamthatha endodeni \add yakhe\add*, kuPalitiyeli indodana kaLayishi\x + 1 Sam. 25.44.\x*.
\v 16 Kodwa indoda yakhe yahamba laye, ihamba ikhala inyembezi ngemva kwakhe kwaze kwaba seBahurimi\x + 16.5. 17.18. 19.16. 1 Kho. 2.8.\x*. UAbhineri wasesithi kuyo: Hamba, buyela. Yasibuyela.
\p
\v 17 UAbhineri wasesiba lenkulumo labadala bakoIsrayeli esithi: Ngezikhathi ezidlulileyo lalifuna uDavida ukuthi abe yinkosi phezu kwenu.
\v 18 Khathesi-ke, \add kw\add*enzeni, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* ikhulumile ngoDavida ukuthi: Ngesandla senceku yami uDavida ngizakhulula abantu bami uIsrayeli esandleni samaFilisti lesandleni sazo zonke izitha zabo\x + 3.9.\x*.
\v 19 UAbhineri wasekhuluma futhi endlebeni zakoBhenjamini\x + 1 Lan. 12.29.\x*; uAbhineri njalo wasesiyakhuluma endlebeni zikaDavida eHebroni konke okwakukuhle emehlweni akoIsrayeli lemehlweni endlu yonke yakoBhenjamini.
\v 20 Ngakho uAbhineri wafika kuDavida eHebroni elamadoda angamatshumi amabili; uDavida wasesenzela uAbhineri lamadoda ayelaye idili.
\v 21 UAbhineri wasesithi kuDavida: Ngizasukuma ngihambe, ngibuthanise uIsrayeli wonke enkosini yami, inkosi, ukuze benze isivumelwano lawe\x + 3.12,13.\x*, lokuthi ubuse kukho konke umphefumulo wakho okufisayo\x + 1 Kho. 11.37.\x*. UDavida waseyekela uAbhineri ukuthi ahambe, wasehamba ngokuthula.
\s UJowabi ubulala uAbhineri
\p
\v 22 Khangela-ke, izinceku zikaDavida loJowabi bafika bevela ekuhlaseleni beza belempango enkulu. Kodwa uAbhineri wayengekho kuDavida eHebroni, ngoba wayemyekele ukuthi ahambe, wahamba ngokuthula.
\v 23 Esefikile uJowabi lebutho lonke elalilaye, bamtshela uJowabi besithi: UAbhineri indodana kaNeri ubefikile enkosini, imyekele wahamba; wahamba ngokuthula.
\v 24 UJowabi wasesiya enkosini, wathi: Wenzeni? Khangela, uAbhineri ubefikile kuwe; pho, umyekeleleni ukuthi ahambe, wahamba lokuhamba?
\v 25 Uyamazi uAbhineri indodana kaNeri ukuthi ulande ukukukhohlisa, lokwazi ukuphuma kwakho lokungena kwakho, lokwazi konke okwenzayo\x + Hez. 43.11. 1 Sam. 29.6.\x*.
\v 26 Esephumile uJowabi kuDavida wathuma izithunywa ukulandela uAbhineri, ezambuyisa emthonjeni weSira; kodwa uDavida wayenga\add kw\add*azi \add lokho\add*.
\v 27 UAbhineri esebuyile eHebroni, uJowabi wamphambulela eceleni phakathi kwesango ukuze akhulume laye ngasese\x + 20.9,10. 1 Kho. 2.5.\x*; wasemtshaya lapho kubambo lwesihlanu waze wafa, ngenxa yegazi likaAsaheli umfowabo\x + 2.23.\x*.
\p
\v 28 Kwathi uDavida esekuzwile emva kwalokho wathi: Mina lombuso wami kasilacala phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuze kube nininini ngegazi likaAbhineri indodana kaNeri.
\v 29 Kalihlale phezu kwekhanda likaJowabi lendlini yonke kayise\x + 1 Kho. 2.32,33.\x*. Kakungaqunywa endlini kaJowabi ogobhozayo\x + Levi 15.2.\x*, kumbe umlephero\x + Levi 14.2. 2 Kho. 5.1.\x*, kumbe odondolozelayo, kumbe owa ngenkemba, kumbe oswela ukudla\x + Zaga 31.19. Eks. 21.19.\x*.
\v 30 Ngokunjalo uJowabi loAbishayi umfowabo bambulala uAbhineri, ngoba wayebulele umfowabo uAsaheli eGibeyoni empini\x + 2.23. 1 Lan. 27.7.\x*.
\p
\v 31 UDavida wasesithi kuJowabi lakubo bonke abantu ababelaye: Dabulani izigqoko zenu\x + 1.2.\x*, libhince amasaka, lilile phambi kukaAbhineri\x + 1 Kho. 20.31.\x*. Inkosi uDavida yasilandela ithala.
\v 32 UAbhineri basebemngcwabela eHebroni; inkosi yasiphakamisa ilizwi layo yakhala inyembezi engcwabeni likaAbhineri, labantu bonke bakhala inyembezi.
\v 33 Inkosi yamenzela uAbhineri isililo\x + 1.17.\x* yathi: Afe uAbhineri njengokufa kwesithutha yini\x + 13.12,13.\x*?
\v 34 Izandla zakho bezingabotshwanga, lenyawo zakho bezingafakwanga emaketaneni; njengowela phambi kwabantu ababi uwile. Bonke abantu basebephinda bemkhalela inyembezi.
\v 35 Bonke abantu basebesiza ukumenza uDavida ukuthi adle ukudla kusesemini\x + 12.17.\x*; kodwa uDavida wafunga esithi: Kenze njalo uNkulunkulu kimi engezelele ngokunjalo\x + 3.9.\x*, uba nginambitha ukudla loba okunye nje lingakatshoni ilanga\x + 1.12.\x*.
\v 36 Kwathi bonke abantu bekunanzelela, kwaba kuhle emehlweni abo; njengakho konke eyakwenzayo inkosi, kwaba kuhle emehlweni abo bonke abantu.
\v 37 Ngoba bonke abantu loIsrayeli wonke bazi ngalolosuku ukuthi kwakungeyisikho okwenkosi ukubulala uAbhineri indodana kaNeri.
\v 38 Inkosi yasisithi encekwini zayo: Kalazi yini ukuthi kuwe induna lomkhulu koIsrayeli lamuhla?
\v 39 Lami lamuhla ngibuthakathaka, njalo ngigcotshwe ngaba yinkosi; lalamadoda, amadodana kaZeruya\x + 1 Sam. 26.6.\x*, alukhuni kulami\x + 19.7.\x*. IN\nd kosi\nd* izavuza umenzi wobubi njengobubi bakhe\x + Hlab. 28.4. 62.12. 2 Tim. 4.14.\x*.
